:45.000Z","msg":"幫巴打推！！！<br />\n咁我想問08年爆煲係因為乜事？<br />\n就係因為債仔爆煲所以保險公司爆煲然後投資者一齊爆煲？"},{"pid":"8d100aa7ae6e3f0670a5fb84c584c660b095946f","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee26d7e6b3f0f3432cbd1112ead6900b4176641f","tid":948963,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"幫巴打推！！！<br />\n咁我想問08年爆煲係因為乜事？<br />\n就係因為債仔爆煲所以保險公司爆煲然後投資者一齊爆煲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"好多嘢同時被觸發<br />\n<br />\n房產泡沫 -&gt;房貸 -&gt;房貸抵押債券 -&gt;銀行有錢賺 -&gt; 保險公司出swap -&gt;投資者（包括機構）擺更多錢 -&gt; 理論上會變咗個循環 -&gt;人錢多又買樓 -&gt;房貸 -&gt;房貸抵押 -&gt; ......<br />\n<br />\n但如果樓價泡沫爆 -&gt;負資產唔還錢 -&gt;MBS違約，保險公司又賠錢，<br />\n一開頭踏咗幾多個循環上去，就落返咁多個<br />\n其中一個角色風險管理做得唔好 摺咗 大家一齊摺"},{"pid":"8b1564f0a025a7ae3c6414b83beef3d280980be2","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867bc0ed0a42d8bf73351b7063734b35d946a31f","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5152c530b8b39dbb8c87ef350038841efb8d7158","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d94f5890b129355e28bab1f8b7839ecb5183013","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d7dc753f24a0e9e7b6307f57d6322f884c7323","tid":948963,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"12d4cc80357ae505713886200e16a6e7d5953b27","tid":948963,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54d7dc753f24a0e9e7b6307f57d6322f88